              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm">NLP</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm">Undergrad</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We introduce Textfocals, a UI prototype designed to investigate a human-centered approach that emphasizes the user's role in writing. Textfocals supports the writing process by providing LLM-generated summaries, questions, and advice in a sidebar, encouraging reflection and self-driven revision while maintaining full authorship.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2403.01055" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
